  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Registry is designed to evaluate use of endolumenal tissue anchors for soft tissue
      approximation to repair a dilated gastric pouch and gastrojejunal anastomosis in
      post-Roux-En-Y gastric bypass patients presenting with weight regain. Registry will also
      assess tissue anchor durability.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
